description: GemBox.Document is a .NET component that enables developers to read, write, convert and print document files (DOCX, DOC, PDF, HTML, XPS, RTF, TXT) from .NET applications in a simple and efficient way.
releaseNotes:
- Added support for 'page-break-before' attribute in HTML reader/writer.
- Added support for PDF Full Screen view.
- Added support for table's left indention when writing HTML files.
- Fixed issue with table borders color/brightness when rendering document.
- Added support for System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage in Save method.
- Added support for SaveOptions.ContentType.
- Fixed various issues with RTF reader/writer for files generated by 3rd visual components.
- Fixed issue with reading DOC with section columns without defined space.
- Fixed issue with importing list paragraphs.
- Added support for reading RTF files produced by DevExpress visual components.
summary: GemBox.Document is a .NET component for reading and writing Word (DOCX, DOC), PDF, XPS, HTML and RTF documents.
